 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Appearance: Reddish-brown, round, film coated tablets, debossed "702" on one side and plain on other side.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>DISPENSE contents with a child-resistant closure (as required) and in a tight container as defined in the USP.</paragraph>
